Alright then.

78
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,600
But I can leave you a phone number.

79
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,920
If you need it,

80
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,280
you can contact them anytime.

81
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,079
Fine.

82
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,840
You finally came out.

83
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:56,140
Did you get the short end of the stick?

84
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,200
Someone did suffer.

85
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,160
But it wasn't me.

86
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,600
That's good.

87
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:03,690
Let's go.

88
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,180
I'll take you home.

89
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,080
Wait.

90
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,440
I have a question.

91
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,600
What?

92
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,160
Do you still want to continue

93
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,320
with the marriage alliance with the Gu family

94
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,640
and marry Gu Nian?

95
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,240
Qiushan,

96
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,880
my brother's greatest wish

97
