268
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,360
If you're worried about Weiwei falling behind in her studies,

269
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,420
you can hire another teacher for her.

270
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:50,960
Don't worry about what happened last night.

271
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,880
Just treat it

272
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,330
as if it were all a dream.

273
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,360
The proud Mr. Mu,

274
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,520
after being slept with

275
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:58,840
and then immediately abandoned,

276
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,280
must be furious.

277
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:01,800
But this way,

278
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:03,960
he won't be able to let me go.

279
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,520
Jiang Chunyu

280
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,319
since you've provoked me

281
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:12,960
don't think about escaping.

282
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:21,880
Hello?

283
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,240
Alright, I got it.

284
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:27,319
Good.

285
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,480
Sis.

286
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:33,520
Jiang Chunyu has already moved away from her previous place.

287
00:17:33,520 --> 00:17:35,320
It seems that although we didn't kill her last time,

288
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:36,640
she's still scared.

289
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,570
What about her job at the Mu family?

290
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:41,840
She quit that too.

291
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,420
They said she took a leave.

292
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,920
